query:
SELECT i.id, i.postUrlId, i.fromAccountId, i.fromDeviceId, i.interactionType, i.status, i.executedAt, i.errorMessage, p.url as postUrl 
FROM interactions i 
LEFT JOIN post_urls p ON i.postUrlId = p.id 
WHERE i.interactionType = 'like' 
ORDER BY i.createdAt DESC 
LIMIT 3;
